---

<style>
  section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--theme-primary-primary) 0%, var(--palette-grey-900) 100%);
    color: var(--theme-primary-on-primary);
    min-height: auto;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    display: grid;
    place-content: center;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--theme-primary-on-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--theme-primary-on-primary);
    color: var(--theme-primary-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .cta-link.secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
  }
  .cta-link:hover {
    background: var(--theme-primary-primary);
    color: var(--theme-primary-on-primary);
  }
  .cta-link.secondary:hover {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--theme-primary-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .cta-link {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-content">
    <h2>Ready to Architect Your Next Phase of Growth?</h2>
    <p>
      Build secure, scalable and intelligent digital ecosystems with confidence.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-link">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      <a href="/about" class="cta-link secondary">Explore Our Capabilities</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
